<i>♪ Please, just let me down ♪</i>

44:21.617 --> 44:28.415
<i>♪ Let me go, but please ♪</i>

44:30.376 --> 44:37.383
<i>♪ Don't leave me in the dark ♪</i>

44:53.357 --> 44:54.900
I don't want you to see Billie...

44:56.402 --> 44:57.403
ever again.

44:58.028 --> 45:04.868
<i>♪ Come meet me in the dark ♪</i>

45:05.577 --> 45:09.206
<i>♪ Please ♪</i>

45:09.206 --> 45:15.921
<i>♪ Come meet me in the dark ♪</i>

